element.name: EXCountError
element.short: Exception raised when a chart source provides less x values than required by a series.

element.name: EYCountError
element.short: Exception raised when a chart source provides less y values than required by a series.

element.name: EEditableSourceRequired
element.short: Exception raised when the chart source assigned to a series is required to be editable, but the current chart source is not.
